divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: On Sunday morning, April 10, 2005 around 5:50 am I went out side and was going to the car when I looked up and there was circular object in the sky overhead .It was a strong orange color. It never moved while I stared at it. I live in a trailer park and the size of it covered the well over the width of the road. I stared at it for a short time .It was lower than most aircraft that fly overhead.No planes I ever saw could stay motionless in the air. It was not the moon. because it was just slighly over the trailers in the trailer Park.It made me wonder what it was.,I went inside after about several minutes of staring at it. All that time it never moved.It had a color orange all around it.. It was a perfect circle. It was very low in the sky. to low for comfort.
